This program does the lexical analysis of a C code.
It carries out tokenization of the input C program and outputs its various types of tokens.

This program is written in C Programming Language.

Requirements:
gcc-compiler to compile and execute the '.c' file

Note:
For the main function choose one of the 3 options available depending on whether your requirement is:
1) Code to be analyzed is input as a predefined array in the code.
2) Code to be analyzed is stored in a file.
3) Code to be analyzed has to be gotten as user input, saved in a file and then read from the file.
